WEBVTT

00:00:01.200 --> 00:00:04.520
When I was a child,
I knew I had superpowers.

00:00:06.920 --> 00:00:08.135
That's right.

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:09.256
(Laughter)

00:00:09.280 --> 00:00:13.296
I thought I was absolutely amazing
because I could understand

00:00:13.320 --> 00:00:15.456
and relate to the feelings
of brown people,

00:00:15.480 --> 00:00:18.880
like my grandfather,
a conservative Muslim guy.

00:00:19.360 --> 00:00:24.256
And also, I could understand
my Afghan mother, my Pakistani father,

00:00:24.280 --> 00:00:28.080
not so religious
but laid-back, fairly liberal.

